# Licensed BodyParts3D meshes (CC BY-SA 2.1 JP) must NEVER be committed. Deny by
# default — only this file and the provenance note are tracked. If you fetch a mesh
# here (see PROVENANCE.md) it stays ignored, so a plain `git add` can't leak it.
# (`git add -f` would still force it in — don't; the documented fetch writes to /tmp,
# outside the repo, so a mesh never lands here in the first place.)
*
!.gitignore
!PROVENANCE.md
